     * Adds groups to a rule
     * @example
     * var rules = new ApprovalRuleBuilder()
     *                 .addRuleSet(ApprovalRuleBuilder.RULESET_APPROVES)
     *                 .addRule(ApprovalRuleBuilder.RULE_ANY)
